readability_reflection: I found string concatenation easier to understand as it read just like math adding strings together.
comprehension_debugging: With the commas and parentheses making unique combinations, it was difficult to understand both sometimes, yet I found concatenation better.
preference_rationale: I would chose concatenation as it would be easier to code because it would be the same thought process as in math.
learning_curve: It helped with understanding what the parantheses and quotation marks mean. With interpolation, the brackets gave me a rough idea what the code ment
